    (home-page "http://www.stat.umn.edu/geyer/aster/")
    (synopsis "Aster Models")
    (description
     "Aster models (Geyer, Wagenius, and Shaw, 2007,
<doi:10.1093/biomet/asm030>; Shaw, Geyer, Wagenius, Hangelbroek, and Etterson,
